on Environment<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>We set a new testing environment and carry your Magento 2 to a new server. Then, we take your data, content and extensions from Magento 1 and transport them to the new version.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We make sure the transition is secure and all your information is transferred without being lost or damaged.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Testing And QA<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our QA team conducts detailed tests while following a thorough migration checklist. Our aim is to ensure all features and functionalities of your Magento 2 e-store work optimally combination with the data migrated from your previous version.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Launch<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, it\u2019s time for launch! Our team launches your new solution equipped with all the benefits of Magento 2 software.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Check out the sleek homepage our Digital Silk designers created for Eurolux Home, below.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This brand-new Magento solution features simple navigation, high-quality imagery, a streamlined shopping and check out process, and more.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image size-full wp-image-5635\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Magento2-migration.jpg\" alt=\"Magento 2 website design\" class=\"wp-image-5635\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">[Source: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.euroluxhome.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Eurolux Home<\/a>]<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h3>Support And Maintenance<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As an additional service outside the scope of your migration project, we offer support and maintenance to make sure your new Magento 2 e-store remains updated and competitive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We fix issues that might arise, install updates, clean broken or non-functioning links and more.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How-To-Migrate-Your-E-store-To-Magento-2-Takeaways\"><\/span>How To Migrate Your E-store To Magento